{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC11_FRE_530.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1b,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Mr. Fred, I went to go ask Marietta what kind of bread she wants to eat!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x144,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Really!? I haven't been able to concentrate enough to bake, so I wasn't sure what I should do."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x146,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Can you tell me right away!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x173,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "A combination of meat and bread...<CR>I've never thought of that before..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x177,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Those usually fall in the domain of pies..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I see... What's the borderline between pie and bread anyway?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x178,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Simply put, they're made differently. You have to leaven dough to make bread."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x179,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "But for pie, you have to use a lot of butter for the dough."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Hearing it like that, they seem like completely different things..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Of course, there are breads that you don't need to leaven the dough, and breads that call for lots of butter."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Flour and water are the basic ingredients for both, so an absolute distinction would be..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Breads are sold at bakeries, and pies are sold at pie shops...I would think."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, that's an easy distinction!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, well you don't have to make a distinction. New ideas are very helpful for making new breads."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "So, did Ms. Marietta mention anything else?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x35,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Well, she said more variety of cute bread will make her happy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Hehehe, so she had the same opinion as me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I see... Mmhm, so females like cute things..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Yes. She said that she likes this shop because there are lots of cute types of bread."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0xd4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Cute...!? Like...what!? I'm not mentally prepared for this, yet..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Oh, but she was worried about how you're so quiet and scary, and that your shop won't flourish."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0xd7,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "S-Scary...? I see, so I am a scary person..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Well, I don't think so, but Marietta seems to think that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "No, it's fine... I'm sure everything she said is true..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, thank you. I'll think of a new bread from what you just told me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x43,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "This is just my way of thanking you,<CR>so please accept it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "You got 500 Cole."
        }
    ]
}